description: Regenerate Redis cache's access keys. This operation requires write permission to the cache resource.

subscription_id.description: Gets subscription credentials which uniquely identify the Microsoft Azure subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every service call.

secondarykey.description: The current secondary key that clients can use to authenticate with Redis cache.

primarykey.description: The current primary key that clients can use to authenticate with Redis cache.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group.

name.description: The name of the Redis cache.
